title: Florida Braces for Hurricane Nicole While Still Recovering From Ian
description: Some communities still recovering from Hurricane Ian are preparing for Florida’s next storm.
dc:creator: Joe Capozzi, Remy Tumin and Rick Rojas
media:credit: Zack Wittman for The New York Times
media:description: Robert McCorrison carried sandbags to his car in Fort Pierce, Fla., on Wednesday, as Hurricane Nicole approached the state’s east coast.
